From: "Y.b. Lu" <yangbo.lu@nxp.com>
Date: Thu, 23 May 2019 02:33:41 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 624/741] arm64: dts: fsl: ls1028a: add ENETC 1588 timer node

commit a9aeb782d8d4b12ce0bc1d7c383726d7710eb678 from
http://source.codeaurora.org/external/qoriq/qoriq-components/linux

Add ENETC 1588 timer node which is ENETC PF 4 (Physiscal Function 4).

Signed-off-by: Yangbo Lu <yangbo.lu@nxp.com>
Signed-off-by: David S. Miller <davem@davemloft.net>
Signed-off-by: Zhantao Tang <zhantao.tang@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls1028a.dtsi | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls1028a.dtsi b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls1028a.dtsi
index 117126e523a1..04fb53fcb176 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls1028a.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-ls1028a.dtsi
@@ -798,6 +798,12 @@
 				compatible = "fsl,enetc";
 				reg = <0x000100 0 0 0 0>;
 			};
+                        ethernet@0,4 {
+                                compatible = "fsl,enetc-ptp";
+                                reg = <0x000400 0 0 0 0>;
+                                clocks = <&clockgen 4 0>;
+                                little-endian;
+                        };
 		};
 
